    <item>
      <title>Chanana：预计美元短期内将走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/chanana-expect-dollar-to-weaken-in-short-term-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[盛宝外汇策略主管 Charu Chanana 表示，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的鸽派言论为 9 月降息敞开了大门，但问题是美联储能降息到什么程度。她补充说，她预计美元今年将受到美联储和美国大选的影响而走弱。Charu Chanana 还在 Horizo​​ns Middle East and Africa 上与 Joumanna Bercetche 讨论了日元和英镑。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/chanana-expect-dollar-to-weaken-in-short-term-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:55:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
